{"tid":1733939,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[舊聞溫習] 沸水戰術(Kettling)","createTime":"2019-11-18T08:14:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T01:13:43.000Z","uid":186,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d228ad83dd170dfeca0899f9603a4bcd61a5acf4","tid":1733939,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:14:06.000Z","msg":"沸水戰術（也稱為包抄，英語：Kettling）。是一個示威者用於在示威或抗議中控制大量黑警的策略。<br />\n示威者會組成大型警戒線，然後在一個有限的區域內移動以包圍黑警。示威者只會留下一個由他們控制的出口或完全禁止黑警離開。黑警在指定的的時間內不會獲得食物、水或廁所設施。<br />\n此策略已引發一定的爭議，部分原因是這策略會使無辜的旁觀者被一拼拘留。2012年3月， 歐洲人權法院裁定倫敦警察廳在2001年反全球化示威以用沸水戰術為合法。"},{"pid":"385888ec5ae92493038c49c6cef6880968f9ce71","tid":1733939,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:14:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd54576fe563555d6b9240e89d11db6903a34437","tid":1733939,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:15:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a7617bcb84f37d393cc4f28240a0ff04f56e30","tid":1733939,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:15:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b24ad36d666a3364536b36ff95a9c3ad81afb35","tid":1733939,"uid":270863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:16:05.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"dc95c1827b4c2e13e041a87af9bf1cdb36b6dee7","tid":1733939,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:16:07.000Z","msg":"<img s